id": "2067952923108118844", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2067952923108118844", "text": "Iran is requiring all vessels that want to pass the strait to fill in a form on: https://t.co/zHUFxI6rau and gain permission prior to passage #OOTT", "time": "12:49", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 82711, "likes": 163, "replies": 13, "retweets": 39, "quotes": 12, "bookmarks": 20, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067953678510604302", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067953678510604302", "text": "Senior US Official: Israel, Hezbollah Have Agreed To A Ceasefire At 16:00 Local Time On Friday\n\n#OOTT", "time": "12:52", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 12882, "likes": 34, "replies": 3, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067955710353113545", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067955710353113545", "text": "A senior American official tells me: Israel and Hezbollah have agreed to a renewed ceasefire starting at 16:00 Israel time. The new agreement was reached through US and Qatar mediation after talks with Israel and Iran.\n\n#OOTT", "time": "13:00", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 9775, "likes": 11, "replies": 4, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067960874132988409", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2067960874132988409", "text": "Sounds like Trump won’t reinstate his blockade on Iranian ships \n\nIf that’s the case it strongly suggests he is fearful of tank bottoms\n\nTank bottoms may be unlikely, but it’s fear of tank bottoms that causes price to spike \n\nHerds don’t react well to fear!  #oott", "time": "13:21", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 4393, "likes": 35, "replies": 3, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067966334210805872", "url": "https://x.com/avionsunantiqu1/status/2067966334210805872", "text": "Think of the odds of Israel leaving Lebanon as equal to the Straits of Hormuz staying open.\n\nThen place time limits on that equation, 1 day, 5 day, 10 day, 30 day, 60 day to establish probabilities.\n\nThen match those with the probabilities of tank bottoms in 30, 60, 90 days #OOTT", "time": "13:42", "author": "avionsunantiqu1", "author_name": "Nicholas James", "followers": 1433, "views": 2233, "likes": 11, "replies": 4, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067973752101433724", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067973752101433724", "text": "Iran Rejects Claims On Closure Of Strait Of Hormuz – Foreign Ministry\n\n#OOTT", "time": "14:12", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 9323, "likes": 19, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067974870558785543", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2067974870558785543", "text": "Pakistan Reports Mine in Strait of Hormuz Area\n#oott", "time": "14:16", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 66495, "likes": 92, "replies": 4, "retweets": 20, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": null}, {"id": "2067999006882508885", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2067999006882508885", "text": "#OOTT | US Intelligence Warns Israel Is Likely To Undermine Iran Peace Deal, Officials Say – @washingtonpost \nhttps://t.co/5aMO9ziniJ", "time": "15:52", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436346, "views": 6793, "likes": 9, "replies": 1, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068007718497955851", "url": "https://x.com/Amalteya3000/status/2068007718497955851", "text": "Imo oil bulls didn't miscalculate; they just jumped the gun.\nseems right now oil has a good chance of surging above 130 around August or September.\n#oott", "time": "16:27", "autho